description:

name: Laptop
description:
Beneficiary is a mechanical and electrical student who requires assistance with procuring a laptop that can support the running of the programmes (e.g. AutoDesk 2026 programs, Microsoft 365 and Google Drive) used in his classes.

His current laptop is also a donated and refurbished one which does not have the capacity to open the files that he needs.

These are the laptop specifications that may support the programmes he needs to use:
- Ryzen 7 7840HS processor (or any of the same/later processors)
- Nvidia RTX 2070ti/3070ti
- 32gb RAM

Do feel free to reach out if any clarification is required to ascertain the suitability of the donated laptop. Thank you!
